      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves multiple operations: parsing XML, inserting, updating, and deleting records. It uses temporary tables and joins, which add to its complexity. The logic is straightforward but requires understanding of XML handling and SQL operations."
        }
